sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as KServe Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant VLLM_HTTP as vLLM HTTP API<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant VLLM_GRPC as vLLM TGIS gRPC<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant GPU as NVIDIA GPU<br/>CUDA
    participant S3 as Model Storage<br/>S3/PVC

    Note over VLLM_HTTP,S3: Flow 3: Model Loading at Startup
    VLLM_HTTP->>S3: Load model weights<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+ or volume mount<br/>Auth: IAM / Service Account
    S3-->>VLLM_HTTP: Model artifacts

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 1: OpenAI-compatible HTTP Inference
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/completions<br/>or /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>VLLM_HTTP: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000 plaintext (pod network)<br/>Auth: None
    VLLM_HTTP->>GPU: CUDA inference call
    GPU-->>VLLM_HTTP: Inference result
    VLLM_HTTP-->>Gateway: JSON Response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 2: TGIS gRPC Inference
    Client->>Gateway: gRPC GenerationService<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>VLLM_GRPC: Forward gRPC request<br/>gRPC/8033 plaintext (pod network)<br/>Auth: None
    VLLM_GRPC->>GPU: CUDA inference call
    GPU-->>VLLM_GRPC: Inference result
    VLLM_GRPC-->>Gateway: gRPC Response
    Gateway-->>Client: gRPC over HTTPS Response
